Incomplete just need to recolor a the gauntlets and the boots. When I finish and if I get good feedback I'll post the mod up. This is really just a Black/Blood Red recolor of my favorite armor mod Emperor's Will.

Darker Color = more shine = better overall look in game.

This mod will of course need Emperors Will itself.
